  <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to DogsRUs</h1>

  <p class="lead">Meet the Team Behind DogsRUs</p>

  <p>We are Team GemCraft, a group of passionate student developers, consisting of Michael and Jaspreet. Our journey began in a Rails development class, where we shared a common love for dogs and a desire to create something special.</p>

  <p>DogsRUs is the result of our shared enthusiasm for dogs and our commitment to delivering a delightful experience for fellow dog enthusiasts. Our mission is to bring dog lovers closer to the wonderful world of canines in a fun and engaging way.</p>

  <h2>What is DogsRUs?</h2>

  <p>DogsRUs is your ultimate destination for all things canine. Our web application is designed with love and care to cater to your dog-loving spirit. Here's what you can expect from our app:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Comprehensive Dog Breed Database:</strong> Explore an extensive list of dog breeds, including their sub-breeds.</li>
    <li><strong>Effortless Breed Search:</strong> Quickly find specific dog breeds by name.</li>
    <li><strong>Random Dog Images:</strong> Enjoy a daily dose of adorable dog pictures to brighten your day.</li>
    <li><strong>Customized Image Search:</strong> Search for dog images by selecting a breed of your choice.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>We are thrilled to present DogsRUs as a user-friendly platform for all dog enthusiasts. Whether you're interested in learning about different dog breeds, finding adorable dog pictures, or simply exploring the canine world, DogsRUs is here for you.</p>

  <p>Thank you for joining us on this journey through the world of dogs!</p>
